--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Type/Byte Orders: (each unknown type will be given a character)
[b]Int16:[/b] Order: [b][little Endian][/b] Bytes: int int >> 8
[b]Int16:[/b] Order: [b][Big Endian][/b] Bytes: int >> 8 int
[b]Int16:[/b] Order: [b][A][/b] Bytes: int >> 8 int + 128
[b]Int32:[/b] Order: [b][A][/b] Bytes: int >> 16 int >> 24 int int >> 8
[b]Int32:[/b] Order: [b][Middle Endian 1][/b] Bytes: int >> 8 int int >> 24 int >> 16
[b]Int32:[/b] Order: [b][little Endian][/b] Bytes: int int >> 8 int >> 16 int >> 24
[b]Int32:[/b] Order: [b][little Endian][/b] Bytes: int >> 24 int >> 16 int >> 8 int
[b]Int64:[/b] Order: [b][Big Endian][/b] Int32 [Big Endian] (2x): // adding 2 integers, not bytes. int64 >> 32 int64 & -1L
[b]Int64:[/b] Order: [b][little Endian][/b] Int32 [little Endian] (2x): // adding 2 integers, not bytes. int64 & -1L int64 >> 32
